<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/6400> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #6400" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Fast. Mag. Vic., Degrassi 283, 288 (P. Cornelius, T. Peducaeus); ibid. 136, 508f. On Cornelius, see PIR² 2.354, no. 1437; 342f., no. 1395." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/6290> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #6290" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Termed by Appian a subordinate commander along with L. Antonius in Spain (BC 5.54). He held command along with a certain Lucius (see above, on Livius; and Promagistrates, on Cornelius Balbus) when Octavian sent Antonius there. He may be either a Sextus Peducaeus or T. Peducaeus, Cos. Suff. 35." .
